Title: General Admission
Description:
It isn't enough to inconvenience Zev'kall. He should be humiliated. I already have some information, but I need more.

He stores military logs in a room that is too tiny for me to access. See what information he's hiding. I'm sure there's potential blackmail material in there somewhere.
ObjectivesText: Find some useful blackmail material for the General.
CompletionText: There should be something I can use.
RewardText:
Let me see!

This... is not blackmail material. But it is far worse.
